Package api.equinix.javasdk.networkedge.client

package api.equinix.javasdk.networkedge.client
Network Edge client interfaces for the Equinix Java SDK. Provides typed access to virtual network device management including Devices, DeviceLinks, SSHUsers, VPNs, BGPPeerings, ACLTemplates, Backups, PublicKeys, DeviceTypes, Accounts, and Metros. Each interface defines CRUD operations appropriate for the resource, enabling provisioning and lifecycle management of Network Edge appliances.
